data.description: Beautiful 2 story home 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home in the Grant Meadows subdivision. This home has high ceilings in the living room area and open floor plan with wood look laminate flooring. The kitchen is open to the living and breakfast area, with formal dining area, or this room could be used for an office. The Primary bedroom is downstairs and has an attached bathroom with 2 sinks and separate shower and tub. The backyard has a large covered porch perfect for backyard BBQ's with plenty of space to run and play in the yard. The upstairs of the home has 3 bedrooms, a full bath, and a game room. Zoned to the highly rated Cypress Fairbanks Schools. Make and appointment today to see this gorgeous home! New mulch and sod coming soon.
